betterquesting:10.desc:8:
§7§oThis gate lets you control the ability to transmit a signal based on another signal.

The data cell has two input-output paths, that work in both directions, a top path and a bottom path.

The top path is a one-input-one-output redstone connection.

The bottom path only transmits redstone if the top path has redstone.

If the top path is tuned off before the bottom path, the bottom output will produre a signal until the top path is turned back on.
